            "value": "<p>You call upon an endless barrage of flames, producing<br>miniature fireballs in your hands to hurl at foes. You cast<br>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.O9w7r4BKgPogYDDe]{Produce Flame} as part of casting flaming fusillade. For the<br>duration of flaming fusillade, Produce Flame’s casting time is<br>reduced from 2 actions to 1.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Heightened (9th)</strong> For the duration, you also gain a status<br>bonus to the damage dealt by Produce Flame equal to<br>flaming fusillade’s spell level.</p>"
